{"tid":1235311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未完！一切都仲未完！","createTime":"2019-06-17T06:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:48:09.000Z","uid":175453,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7355db057f2888c95ee7b719feaebe184070caac","tid":1235311,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"大家唔好覺得 林奠出左封信道歉 政府話暫緩 我地就贏左。我地唔單止未贏 仲係未贏過！平手都未算呀！唔好鬆懈住呀咁多位！唔可以比我地香港既英雄白白犧牲<br />\n我地既要求好簡單<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n1:徹回惡法<br />\n2:釋放所有義士兼不秋後算賬<br />\n3:警狗向市民道歉<br />\n4:林奠下台<br />\n5:追究殺人警犬<br />\n6:阻止國歌法二讀<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家係一樣都未做到！林奠依然漠視民意！大家千萬唔好比佢消磨到鬥智 ！加上黎緊仲有國歌法（7月3日）！要同佢玩到底<br />\n<br />\n但問題係 依家好多人冇曬方向，歷經左一個禮拜既抗爭，唔知跟住點做好。<br />\n<br />\n我認為，呢個禮拜應該作為一個休養期，打文宣戰，比各義士休息同思考未來方向兼比一個deadline 比政府。話比佢知我地既決心。明確既限期必須定於g20峰會前，必須令中央無力全心對付香港，否則過左g20，中央焦點將會放係香港，百害而無一利。<br />\n<br />\n作為限期，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只能選擇今個星期五</span></span><br />\n原因有4：<br />\n1:最後一個係28號前既星期日<br />\n2:民意尚未消退<br />\n3:3毛未有足夠時間滲透主戰線連登<br />\n4:g phone 重返戰線 <br />\n<br />\n假若政府未有讓步，我地要做既係<br />\n係星期日圍堵禮賓府<br />\n兼於星期一衝擊禮賓府！<br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得政府過幾個月會放過班義士 當香港人唔記得左件事之後 你覺得政府會唔會拎班人出黎祭旗？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該咁多位唔好令烈士白白 犧牲呀dllm</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d80aed5ad90a6c83e1cade0ad28d00940bd49fc","tid":1235311,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:06:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b968c4b23ec83594f6d61a9de6b3aa1d92c9a0b7","tid":1235311,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d074b69bcfe9f3a0211ffec49d4deaf96d513a4d","tid":1235311,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4dcd73d4ebf84153bd4713ee2354e9aec0118e39","tid":1235311,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"456895062f68cd23f07e4d1e370bdae8fa5019c1","tid":1235311,"uid":259851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44e3e247d752c55801bee45e0ddf156739012bac","tid":1235311,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a28578836bf18843a0a57d125c26809a0aa0f6b","tid":1235311,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:16:23.000Z","msg":"場仗未完㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db5234bb057ce58c21a1bb48e303704cbb08c3b","tid":1235311,"uid":242400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2956b4c3040689c23cfcb2804886ff16fbb74ad2","tid":1235311,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rs7SFkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frs7SFkd.jpg&h=c15f710b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a3cda0c1de201f84e1be3e1358d0391e2d6baab","tid":1235311,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit